query.sfwSql: --PIR 869 SELECT TOP(1) CASE WHEN SPBX.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE <> 'LIFE' THEN PHH.PAYMENT_DATE ELSE SBA.RETIREMENT_DATE END PAYMENT_DATE FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION SBA INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL SBAD ON SBA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID = SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX ON SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID WHERE SBA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SPBX.PLAN_ID = 1 AND BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('DDPR') ORDER BY PHH.PAYMENT_DATE

SELECT YEAR(PHH.PAYMENT_DATE) AS [YEAR], SUM(CASE WHEN PIT.ITEM_TYPE_DIRECTION = 1 AND ((PAYMENT_1099R_FLAG = 'Y' AND VENDOR_FLAG= 'N') OR ITEM_TYPE_CODE IN ('ITEM46','ITEM47','ITEM45','ITEM56')) THEN ISNULL(PHDE.AMOUNT,0.0) WHEN (ALLOW_ROLLOVER_CODE_VALUE = 'RRED' OR ITEM_TYPE_CODE IN ('ITEM53','ITEM41','ITEM42','ITEM43')) THEN ISNULL(PHDE.AMOUNT,0.0) * PIT.ITEM_TYPE_DIRECTION ELSE 0 END) AS AMOUNT,SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL PHDE ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHDE.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DISTRIBUTION PHD ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT ON PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PHDE.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID AND PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE <> 'ITEM54' INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA ON SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR X ON X.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID AND X.PLAN_ID = 1 INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT P ON P.PERSON_ID = SPBA.PERSON_ID AND P.PLAN_ID = 1 LEFT OUTER JOIN ( SELECT d.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID,CHILD_SUPPORT_FLAG,EMERGENCY_ONETIME_PAYMENT_FLAG, WITHDRAWAL_TYPE_VALUE FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL D INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION B ON D.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID = B.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID )ABA ON SPA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = ABA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID WHERE P.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = @PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND PHD.DISTRIBUTION_STATUS_VALUE NOT IN ('CDRE' ,'CNLD','RCMD') AND (SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' OR (ABA.CHILD_SUPPORT_FLAG = 'Y' AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'WDRL') OR (ABA.EMERGENCY_ONETIME_PAYMENT_FLAG = 'Y' AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'WDRL') OR (ABA.WITHDRAWAL_TYPE_VALUE LIKE 'HS%' AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'WDRL') ) GROUP BY YEAR(PHH.PAYMENT_DATE),SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE

SELECT DISTINCT H.* FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION SBA INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL SBAD ON SBA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID = SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_CALCULATION_HEADER H ON H.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID = SBA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID WHERE H.CALCULATION_TYPE_VALUE = 'FINL' AND H.STATUS_VALUE = 'APPR' AND SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = @BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID AND (SBA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID IS NULL OR SBA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = 0) --PIR 19

--PIR 19 SELECT TOP(1) CASE WHEN SPBX.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE <> 'LIFE' THEN PHH.PAYMENT_DATE ELSE SBA.RETIREMENT_DATE END PAYMENT_DATE FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION SBA INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL SBAD ON SBA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID = SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA ON SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX ON SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID WHERE SBA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SPBX.PLAN_ID = 1 AND FUNDS_TYPE_VALUE = @FUNDS_TYPE_VALUE AND BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('DDPR') ORDER BY PHH.PAYMENT_DATE

SELECT YEAR(PHH.PAYMENT_DATE) AS [YEAR], SUM(CASE WHEN PIT.ITEM_TYPE_DIRECTION = 1 AND ((PAYMENT_1099R_FLAG = 'Y' AND VENDOR_FLAG= 'N') OR ITEM_TYPE_CODE IN ('ITEM46','ITEM47','ITEM45','ITEM56')) THEN ISNULL(PHDE.AMOUNT,0.0) WHEN (ALLOW_ROLLOVER_CODE_VALUE = 'RRED' OR ITEM_TYPE_CODE IN ('ITEM53','ITEM41','ITEM42','ITEM43')) THEN ISNULL(PHDE.AMOUNT,0.0) * PIT.ITEM_TYPE_DIRECTION ELSE 0 END) AS AMOUNT,SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL PHDE ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHDE.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DISTRIBUTION PHD ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT ON PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PHDE.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID AND PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE <> 'ITEM54' INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA ON SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR X ON X.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID AND X.PLAN_ID = 1 INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT P ON P.PERSON_ID = SPBA.PERSON_ID AND P.PLAN_ID = 1 INNER JOIN ( SELECT d.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID,CHILD_SUPPORT_FLAG FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL D INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION B ON D.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID = B.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID AND B.DRO_APPLICATION_ID IS NOT NULL )ABA ON SPA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = ABA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID WHERE P.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = @PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND PHD.DISTRIBUTION_STATUS_VALUE NOT IN ('CDRE' ,'CNLD','RCMD') AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'WDRL' AND SPBA.FUNDS_TYPE_VALUE = @FUNDS_TYPE_VALUE GROUP BY YEAR(PHH.PAYMENT_DATE),SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE
